_sText:
Small, 2 level Gun Game map designed around a mini rocket silo.

Balanced spawns / sides

Supports 32 players

Nasty falls for the un-aware :P

Changelog
========

* V2 1st May 2009
        - resized for better playability
        - removed the spawn 'hallways' from map completely
        - renamed to simply gg_rocket

* v1.1  5th December 2008
           - optimised lightmaps
	   - fixed textures
	   - fixed light errors
	   - fixed prop errors


* v1 	- 3rd Devember 2008
	- First full public release

Credits
=====
Thanks to Ruff for his initial testing :)
